As a bonus action, you can speak the word "Away" and  you will be launched 30 feet in the direction the blade is pointing. This ability has no safeguards or precautions; each jump requires a DEX saving throw to land successfully. [[footnote]]A 15+ is a clean success, 10+ causes you to take 1d4 bludgeoning damage, 5+ you take 1d4 bludgeoning and land prone, and less than 5 you land prone with 1d20 bludgeoning damage.[[/footnote]]

